text: Chaos is when something unpredictable or random happens. It may refer to several different things: * Chaos magic, a branch of occultism * Chaos (mythology), the concept in classical creation stories * Randomness, a lack of intelligible pattern or combination * Chaos theory, a branch of mathematics and physics * Chaos (genus), a type of giant amoeba * 19521 Chaos, a Trans- Neptunian Kuiper belt object in space * K-os, Canadian musician *Chaos an American hip hop Recoring artist == Related pages == * Anarchy * Confusion * Disorder * Order
title: Chaos
